Subject: Blowing Oil

I had the same problem a few weeks ago and it was oil leaking out of my oil
pressure sending unit.  It was dripping and hitting the pully causing oil to
be flung all over.  It was leaking out of the top of the sending unit.  I
put in a new one and the problem quit.
Thomas '67 westy

